to the readable one.\n",[52,155,157,160,162],{"class":54,"line":156},11,[52,158,159],{"class":88},"  unescape",[52,161,102],{"class":92},[52,163,106],{"class":105},[52,165,167],{"class":54,"line":166},12,[52,168,169],{"class":75},"  # Preload the search data when the page loads.\n",[52,171,173,176,178],{"class":54,"line":172},13,[52,174,175],{"class":88},"  preload",[52,177,102],{"class":92},[52,179,106],{"class":105},[16,181,182,183,186,187,190],{},"只需要將 ",[49,184,185],{},"enable"," 改成 ",[49,188,189],{},"true"," 就可以讓自己網站資源搜尋功能囉。",[16,192,193],{},[194,195],"img",{"alt":196,"src":197},"呈現效果","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-09-06%2023.11.23.png",[16,199,200],{},"如果你是早期的版本，可能會需要設置要生成 xml 檔案還是 json 檔案，在新版的 NexT 都是統一生成 json，因為檔案比較小。",[12,202,204],{"id":203},"bookmark","Bookmark",[16,206,207,208,211],{},"Bookmark 是一個書籤套件，它會紀錄你在哪一個頁跳出，只需要一個點擊，你就可以跳回到你上一次離開的畫面，那麼由於 Bookmark 套件並沒有內建安裝在 NexT 中，而且它並沒有上 npm 因此只能夠透過 GitHub clone 下來，你只需要將終端機移動到 ",[49,209,210],{},"themes\u002Fnext"," 後輸入以下指令即可安裝完畢",[42,213,215],{"className":44,"code":214,"language":46,"meta":47,"style":47},"cd themes\u002Fnext\n\u002F\u002F 請務必確認已經在 next 主題目錄下載輸入以下指令\ngit clone https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Ftheme-next\u002Ftheme-next-bookmark.git source\u002Flib\u002Fbookmark\n",[49,216,217,222,227],{"__ignoreMap":47},[52,218,219],{"class":54,"line":55},[52,220,221],{},"cd themes\u002Fnext\n",[52,223,224],{"class":54,"line":79},[52,225,226],{},"\u002F\u002F 請務必確認已經在 next 主題目錄下載輸入以下指令\n",[52,228,229],{"class":54,"line":85},[52,230,231],{},"git clone https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Ftheme-next\u002Ftheme-next-bookmark.git source\u002Flib\u002Fbookmark\n",[16,233,234],{},"接下來只要你點一下你畫面上圖上小書籤就可以跳回上次離開的畫面囉",[16,236,237],{},[194,238],{"alt":239,"src":240},"小書籤","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-09-10%2021.29.08.png",[16,242,243],{},"(但是我印象在 localhost 測試是沒有效果的。)",[12,245,246],{"id":246},"theme-next-reading-progress",[16,248,249],{},"這個套件是一個閱讀進度條套件，目前來講目前來講主要是幫助使用者了解還剩下多少內容，因為這個套件比較沒有什麼，所以就直接來看安裝指令吧",[42,251,253],{"className":44,"code":252,"language":46,"meta":47,"style":47},"cd themes\u002Fnext\n\u002F\u002F 請務必確認已經在 next 主題目錄下載輸入以下指令\ngit clone https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Ftheme-next\u002Ftheme-next-reading-progress source\u002Flib\u002Freading_progress\n",[49,254,255,259,263],{"__ignoreMap":47},[52,256,257],{"class":54,"line":55},[52,258,221],{},[52,260,261],{"class":54,"line":79},[52,262,226],{},[52,264,265],{"class":54,"line":85},[52,266,267],{},"git clone https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Ftheme-next\u002Ftheme-next-reading-progress source\u002Flib\u002Freading_progress\n",[16,269,270,271,273,274,277,278,186,280,282],{},"接下來到 ",[49,272,63],{}," 搜尋 ",[49,275,276],{},"reading_progress","，然後將 ",[49,279,185],{},[49,281,189],{}," 即可",[42,284,286],{"className":66,"code":285,"language":68,"meta":47,"style":47},"reading_progress:\n  enable: true\n  color: \"#37c6c0\"\n  height: 2px\n",[49,287,288,294,303,313],{"__ignoreMap":47},[52,289,290,292],{"class":54,"line":55},[52,291,276],{"class":88},[52,293,93],{"class":92},[52,295,296,298,300],{"class":54,"line":79},[52,297,99],{"class":88},[52,299,102],{"class":92},[52,301,302],{"class":105},"true\n",[52,304,305,308,310],{"class":54,"line":85},[52,306,307],{"class":88},"  color",[52,309,102],{"class":92},[52,311,312],{"class":129},"\"#37c6c0\"\n",[52,314,315,318,320],{"class":54,"line":96},[52,316,317],{"class":88},"  height",[52,319,102],{"class":92},[52,321,322],{"class":129},"2px\n",[16,324,325],{},"開啟之後閱讀文章時，就可以看到上面會多一條進度條囉",[16,327,328],{},[194,329],{"alt":330,"src":331},"進度條","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-09-10%2021.54.08.png",[16,333,334],{},"那麼今天鐵人賽就